#### stressweek_crossed.csv - CBD drinks and stress levels: Version 3<br><span class="tag">\#longitudinal</span><span class="tag">\#more-complex-groupings</span>

As for Version 1 of this study (see above), with 20 staff members from the Psychology department, but instead of taking a measurement _only_ on a self-report scale, we took 10 different measures every time point (cortisol levels, blood pressure, heart rate variability, various questionnaires etc).  

